sentences.english: "Not many would bother with your toothache, " Davo said.
sentences.chinese: 没有多少人会为你的牙痛操心的。

sentences.english: This invention provides a kind of pure Chinese pharmaceutics to cure toothache and its preparation method.
sentences.chinese: 本发明提供一种纯中药剂的治牙痛药物及其制备方法。

sentences.english: It also helps relieve toothaches and gingivitis.
sentences.chinese: 它还有助于缓解牙痛和齿龈炎。

sentences.english: He gets irritable when he's got toothache.

sentences.english: 014 love and toothache have many cures, but none infallible, except possession and dispossession.
sentences.chinese: 爱情和牙痛有多种疗法，但无一可靠，除非要么留着。

sentences.english: Love conquers all things except poverty and toothache.
sentences.chinese: 因此，爱情战无不胜，只战不胜贫穷与牙痛。

sentences.english: Toothaches can be naturally soothed by making a clove paste with cloves and water to rub on the affected area.
sentences.chinese: 牙痛可以自然缓解而作出的丁香，水丁香贴擦于患处。

sentences.english: When you have a toothache, you immediately call the dentist.
sentences.chinese: 当你牙痛的时候要立即看牙医。

sentences.english: His face was swollen up with toothache.
sentences.chinese: 由于牙痛，他的脸都肿起来了。

sentences.english: As for the juice thicker the "Neep Neep" toothbrush would help to alleviate the toothache.

sentences.english: He suffered torments from his aching teeth.
I have a toothache and have to go to the - dentist's (office) every other day.
sentences.chinese: 我患了牙痛必须每隔一天到牙医那里去。

sentences.english: The toothache puffed out one side of his face.
sentences.chinese: 牙痛使他的半边脸肿了起来。

sentences.english: How long have you had your toothache?
